data.description: You can own this fantastic, move-in ready home cheaper than rent! This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is located in a country setting but offers all the amenities of living in town. The large living room is open to the dining room which features storage and the laundry closet. Enter the large, bright kitchen with a great view of the back yard. The utility closet offers lots of extra space for storage or a pantry. Step onto the back deck and into your beautiful backyard offering a 17,100 square foot lot for the kids to play and to have a summer evening bonfire! This great property also offers a storage building, 18x20 barn and 10x10 dog kennel. You'll enjoy your evenings on the covered front porch that offers stunning sunset views.
